div.div:
ShoppingCart will only add items when not completed. adding will also set total and tax to Double.NaN.
Calculate will always calculate unless complete is true.
CompletedTransactionException will be thrown whenever ShoppingCart has been completed to prevent double buying.
total and tax will have an initial value of Double.NaN. calculateFinalTotal() will run calculateTotal() and calculateTax() if total and tax equal Double.NaN respectively. if calculateTotal or calculateTax are called while complete is true, then they will return total and tax. calculateTotal nor calculateTax should never return Double.NaN. Instead throw an Error.
